NIKO SEMICONDUCT said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 18.71% to NT$244,993,000 from NT$301,396,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            244,993          301,396    
YOY%             -18.71%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,089,528        1,591,874   
YOY%             -31.56% 
=================================================================
 